00221 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::CompareHeaderData()
00222 {
00223         // Check all header values
00224         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetVersion() == calvinCel->GetVersion());
00225         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCols() == calvinCel->GetCols());
00226         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetRows() == calvinCel->GetRows());
00227         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumCells() == calvinCel->GetNumCells());
00228 
00229         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetHeader() == L"");
00230         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetAlg() == calvinCel->GetAlgorithmName());
00231         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetChipType() == calvinCel->GetArrayType());
00232 
00233         ParameterNameValueTypeVector algParams;
00234         calvinCel->GetAlgorithmParameters(algParams);
00235 
00236         // Test GetParams and GetAlgorithmParameters
00237         std::wstring calvinParamString;
00238         for (ParameterNameValueTypeIt ci = algParams.begin(); ci != algParams.end(); ++ci)
00239         {
00240                 // This is a repeat of the calvin adapter implementation, oh well, a file change will not break it
00241                 if (algParams.begin() != ci)
00242                         calvinParamString += L";";
00243                 calvinParamString += ci->GetName();
00244                 calvinParamString += L":";
00245                 calvinParamString += ci->ToString();
00246         }
00247         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinParamString == fusionCel->GetParams());
00248         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinParamString == fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameters());
00249 
00250         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters() == (int)algParams.size());
00251         int paramCount = fusionCel->GetNumberAlgorithmParameters();
00252         ParameterNameValueTypeIt ci = algParams.begin();
00253         for (int ip = 0; ip < paramCount && ci != algParams.end(); ++ip, ++ci)
00254         {
00255                 wstring fusionParamTag = fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameterTag(ip);
00256                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->GetName() == fusionParamTag);
00257                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ci->ToString() == fusionCel->GetAlgorithmParameter(fusionParamTag.c_str()));
00258         }
00259 
00260         // Test GetParameters
00261         FusionTagValuePairTypeList& fusionList = fusionCel->GetParameters();
00262         std::list<FusionTagValuePairType>::iterator fi = fusionList.begin();
00263 
00264         int32_t pi = 0;
00265         int32_t algParamCnt = (int32_t)algParams.size();
00266 
00267         for (; fi != fusionList.end() && pi < algParamCnt; ++fi, ++pi)
00268         {
00269                 std::wstring t1 = fi->Tag;
00270                 std::wstring v1 = fi->Value;
00271                 std::wstring t2 = algParams.at(pi).GetName();
00272                 std::wstring v2 = algParams.at(pi).ToString();
00273                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->Tag == algParams.at(pi).GetName());
00274                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->Value == algParams.at(pi).ToString());
00275                 if (fi->DetailedType().GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType)
00276                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->DetailedType().GetValueFloat() == algParams.at(pi).GetValueFloat());
00277                 else if (fi->DetailedType().GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type)
00278                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fi->DetailedType().GetValueInt32() == algParams.at(pi).GetValueInt32());
00279         }
00280 
00281         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetCellMargin() == 2);
00282 
00283         XYCoordVector outlierCoords;
00284         calvinCel->GetOutlierCoords(outlierCoords);
00285         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumOutliers() == (int)outlierCoords.size());
00286 
00287         XYCoordVector maskCoords;
00288         calvinCel->GetMaskedCoords(maskCoords);
00289         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionCel->GetNumMasked() == (int)maskCoords.size());
00290 
00291         CompareGrids();
00292 }

00294 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::ComparePartialDatHeaders()
00295 {
00296         // Find the parent DAT
00297         GenDataHdrVectorIt begin, end; 
00298         calvinCel->GetFileHeader()->GetGenericDataHdr()->GetParentIterators(begin, end);
00299         std::wstring datHeader;
00300         u_int16_t maxPixel = 0, minPixel = 0;
00301 
00302         for (GenDataHdrVectorIt ii = begin; ii != end; ++ii)
00303         {
00304                 if (ii->GetFileTypeId() == SCAN_ACQUISITION_DATA_TYPE)
00305                 {
00306                         // found the right header, now look for the parameter
00307                         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00308                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(DAT_HEADER_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00309                         {
00310                                 datHeader = nvt.GetValueText();
00311                         }
00312                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(MAX_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00313                         {
00314                                 if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00315                                         maxPixel = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00316                         }
00317 
00318                         if (ii->FindNameValParam(MIN_PIXEL_INTENSITY_PARAM_NAME, nvt))
00319                         {
00320                                 if (nvt.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::UInt16Type)
00321                                         minPixel = nvt.GetValueUInt16();
00322                         }
00323                 }
00324         }
00325 
00326         u_int32_t expectedMax = 0, expectedMin = 0;     // Needs to be a 4 byte int to keep swscanf from messing up the stack frame.
00327         std::wstring fusionDatHeader = fusionCel->GetDatHeader();
00328         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fusionDatHeader.find(datHeader, 0) != wstring::npos);
00329         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(swscanf(fusionDatHeader.c_str(), L"[%d..%d]", &expectedMin, &expectedMax) == 2);
00330         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(minPixel == expectedMin);
00331         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(maxPixel == expectedMax);
00332 
00333 }

00335 void FusionCELDataCalvinTest::CompareGrids()

00340         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDULX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));

00342         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDULY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00343         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperleft.y);
00344 
00345         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDURX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00346         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperright.x);
00347         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDURY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00348         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.upperright.y);
00349 
00350         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLRX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00351         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerright.x);
00352         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLRY_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00353         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerright.y);
00354 
00355         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calvinCel->FindAlgorithmParameter(GRIDLLX_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00356         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetValueFloat() == fusionGrid.lowerleft.x);
